4
00:00:22,625 --> 00:00:24,291
[ Groans ]

5
00:00:24,375 --> 00:00:26,583
Oh, that really hurt.

6
00:00:26,666 --> 00:00:28,166
[ Sighs ]

7
00:00:28,583 --> 00:00:30,375
My foot.

8
00:00:30,458 --> 00:00:32,416
Huh?

9
00:00:33,666 --> 00:00:34,500
I...

10
00:00:34,583 --> 00:00:35,791
[ Drop echoes ]

11
00:00:36,916 --> 00:00:37,958
[ Gasps ]

12
